    "updated_at": "2014-01-24T21:36:45Z",
    "body": "Hm, sounds like we shouldn't be doing this. I also appear to have a misconception of what SO_REUSEADDR is, so for now I think we should leave these as-is.\n\nI don't like the spurious failures, but with this in mind we should probably pursue another fix.\n",
